    <notes>
      <change from="1.18" to="1.19">
        <item><para>Fixed copyright notice in some files</para></item>
        <items name="Implementation">
          <item><para>fixed minor vulnerabilities</para></item>
          <item><para>removed cosmetic comparation with zero in floating
point</para></item>
        </items>
      </change>

      <change from="1.17" to="1.18">
        <items name="Implementation">
          <item><para>All errors moved to fatal, since there is no easy
recovery strategy</para></item>
          <item><para>Vulnerability fixes on cmsio1.c</para></item>
          <item><para>Status check, many functions now check the status when
calling other functions. Improved robustness against ill-formed
profiles.</para></item>
          <item><para>_cmsSaveProfile didn't copy tags from a file based
profile, fixed.</para></item>
        </items>

        <items name="Utilities">
          <item><para>icctrans: CMYKcm support wrongly implemented,
fixed.</para></item>
          <item><para>icclink: linking 3 to 7 channels didn't work in some
cases, fixed.</para></item>
        </items>
      </change>
    </notes>
  </program>
</programs>
